item.title: Peter Sarsgaard - 'September 5' & 'Presumed Innocent'
item.description: The veteran character actor describes his accidental path to acting, working with brother-in-law Jake Gyllenhaal over the years and the pair of films about journalistic ethics that feature some of his finest performances.
